notes: "Source: my own recommendation during the template-gaps-sboxdevkit session (2026-04-16). The stub methods doc explicitly names this initiative as its successor. Research outputs feed both Initiative #2 (ranking/selection gates) and Initiative #3 (Sauron split) — those initiatives should use the validated methods doc as a design lens."
